usic/baek-yerin-new-york-concert-cancelled-covid-19-3470321">白艺潾因 COVID-19 检测呈阳性而取消纽约演唱会的消息</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
